<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="24" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="23" pageNumber="24">The species is easily recognized by its white colony color, rather smooth polyp sclerites, and presence of spindles only.</paragraph>
